parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the transmission can cause the vehicle to stall, jerk, or hesitate while driving, leading to accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: Transmission slippage
hesitation
jerking
failure to accelerate
stalling
loud abnormal sounds
and illumination of the check engine warning indicator.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the ignition system can cause the engine to stall, leading to accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: Engine stalling
intermittent engine shutdown
and failure to start.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Unintended acceleration can cause accidents or loss of control of the vehicle.
symptoms: Sudden acceleration
failure to stop
and loss of control of the vehicle.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Vehicle theft and break-in can result in loss of personal property and damage to the vehicle.
symptoms: Vehicle break-in
theft of personal property
and damage to the vehicle.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of airbags to deploy in the event of an accident can lead to serious injury or death.
symptoms: Airbags fail to deploy in the event of an accident
resulting in injuries or fatalities.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Failure to properly repair airbag recalls can lead to airbag failure, resulting in serious injury or death.
symptoms: Airbag warning light remains illuminated after recall repair
airbag partially inflates under the dash
or airbag fails to deploy in the event of an accident.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Illumination of the SRS light can indicate a problem with the airbag system, which can lead to airbag failure in the event of an accident.
symptoms: SRS light remains illuminated on the dashboard
indicating a problem with the airbag system.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Electrical system failures can cause various safety issues, including the risk of fire, loss of vehicle control, and failure of critical safety systems such as airbags and anti-lock brakes.
symptoms: The clock backlight does not work
the gear shift console backlight goes out
the backlighting for the climate controls has gone out
the SRS warning light stays on
the airbag warning light illuminates on the instrument panel
the vehicle's electrical system malfunctions
and the power lock actuator malfunctions.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Ignition Switch and Key Interlock System Failures
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Ignition switch and key interlock system failures can cause the vehicle to roll away or stall, leading to accidents or injuries.
symptoms: The key becomes dislodged from the ignition switch
the key can be removed from the ignition while the vehicle is in gear
the vehicle rolls away or stalls
and the ignition switch malfunctions.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Airbag system failures can cause the airbags to fail to deploy in a crash, leading to serious injuries or fatalities.
symptoms: The SRS warning light stays on
the airbag warning light illuminates on the instrument panel
the driver's side seat belt detection mechanism fails to function properly
and the airbag inflators are defective.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Power window master switch failures can cause the windows to malfunction, leading to safety risks and potential fires.
symptoms: The power window master switch fails to function properly
the windows do not roll down or up
and the driver's side power window master switch has a warm feeling and stopped functioning.
